The paper discusses process modeling in software engineering, which is a core topic in the field of software engineering. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the object-oriented methodology, which falls under cs.PL (Programming Languages). The Thinging Machine (TM) introduced in the paper has elements of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper discusses the possibility of developing a new method in PM, which falls under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
